OL,3,COfcom investigating GB News programme
OL,4,Cwith Rishi Sunak
OL,6,FThe regulator released a statement on
OL,7,FX, stating: "We are investigating
OL,8,Funder rules 5.11 and 5.12 of the
OL,9,FBroadcasting Code which provide
OL,10,Fadditional due impartiality
OL,11,Frequirements for programmes dealing
OL,12,Fwith matters of major political
OL,13,Fcontroversy and major matters relating
OL,14,Fto current public policy."
