OL,6,FIn the statement Ofcom added that
OL,7,Fthose rules "require that an
OL,8,Fappropriately wide range of
OL,9,Fsignificant views must be included and
OL,10,Fgiven due weight in such programmes,
OL,11,For in clearly linked and timely
OL,12,Fprogrammes".
OL,14,FMr Sunak's spokesperson said he
OL,15,Fdoesn't regret appearing on the
OL,16,Fprogramme: "the prime minister
OL,17,Fundertakes interviews from a range of
OL,18,Fbroadcasters, outlets and other media.
