OL,3,COfcom investigating GB News programme
OL,4,Cwith Rishi Sunak
OL,6,F"Media appearances such as the one he
OL,7,Fconducted last week are an important
OL,8,Fpart of the democratic process."
OL,10,FHe added: "This is obviously a matter
OL,11,Ffor Ofcom, who's rightly an
OL,12,Findependent regulator."
OL,14,FNo politicians from other parties
OL,15,Fappeared on the programme alongside Mr
OL,16,FSunak, and the Labour Party weren't
OL,17,Fgiven an opportunity to respond on the
OL,18,Fprogramme to comments by the prime
OL,19,Fminister.
