OL,3,COfcom investigating GB News programme
OL,4,Cwith Rishi Sunak
OL,6,FHowever, presenter Stephen Dixon said
OL,7,Fduring the programme they had invited
OL,8,FLabour leader Sir Keir Starmer to
OL,9,Fappear in another 'People's Forum' on
OL,10,Fthe channel.
OL,12,FThe Ofcom code states that the "wide
OL,13,Frange" of views can be expressed in
OL,14,Fother programmes as part of a
OL,15,Fchannel's scheduling, as long as they
OL,16,Fare "clearly linked and timely".
