OL,3,COfcom investigating GB News programme
OL,4,Cwith Rishi Sunak
OL,6,FDuring the broadcast, Mr Dixon said
OL,7,Fthe questions to be asked by undecided
OL,8,Fvoters had not been seen in advance by
OL,9,Fthe prime minister or by GB News.
OL,11,FGB News is currently being
OL,12,Finvestigated by Ofcom for a number of
OL,13,Fother shows, including many over
OL,14,Fimpartiality issues.
OL,16,FThe issue of political figures such as
OL,17,FConservative MPs Sir Jacob Rees-Mogg
OL,18,Fand former Conservative deputy
OL,19,Fchairman Lee Anderson presenting
OL,20,Ftopical programmes has also been
OL,21,Fcontentious.
